  1. Simulate a time series of length T=2000 from this model. Create a time series plot. Compute the lag-1, lag-2, and lag-3 sample autocorrelations
set.seed(1)
T <- 2000
#rt = 0.01 + 0.6rt1  0.4rt2 + at
a_t <- rnorm(n=T, mean=0, sd=sqrt(0.02))

r_t <- 0.01 + arima.sim(model=list(order=c(2, 0, 0), ar=c(0.6, -.4)),n =T) + a_t

Lets now create a time series plot

plot.ts(r_t)

Sample autocorrelation plot

acf <- acf(r_t)

acf
